After that, sleep. Being fresh and confident in the discussion will help more than trying to learn advanced AI frameworks overnight. The fact that they specifically want developers with Performance Engineering knowledge suggests they're likely looking for people who understand the domain and can grow into the product, not experts who already know everything.
